The paper discusses improvements to deep learning models for computer vision tasks, specifically by incorporating biologically inspired concepts. This suggests that the paper is likely to fall under the categories of neural networks (cs.NE), computer vision (cs.CV), and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of feedback and integration of sensory information, which could fall under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and systems and control (cs.SY).
